1. *Otkad* se ova situacija dogodila, osećam se izgubljeno. (Ever since this situation happened, I have been feeling lost.)
2. Naše druženje traje *otkad* smo se upoznali. (Our friendship has been going on since we met each other.)
3. On nije napustio grad *otkad* je došao. (He hasn't left the city since he came.)
4. Ona je uzbuđena *otkad* je čula novost. (She has been excited ever since she heard the news.)
5. *Otkad* je postao deo ove kompanije, on je dosta napredovao. (Since he became part of this company, he has made a lot of progress.)